An alternative of RMeCabC

Source: R/compat-rmecab.R
gbs_c.Rd

An alternative of RMeCabC

gbs_c(df, pull = "token", names = "POS1")

Arguments

df

A prettified data.frame of tokenized sentences.
pull

A column name of `df`.
names

A column name of `df`.

Value

A list of named vectors.

See also

Other gibasa: gbs_as_tokens(), gbs_collocate(), gbs_dfm(), gbs_freq()

Examples

xml <- ppn_parse_xml(system.file("sample.xml", package = "pipian"))
gbs_c(xml)
